<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 22:05:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>麦卡锡成为有史以来第一位在众议院投票中被罢免的议长</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/mccarthy-becomes-first-speaker-ever-to-be-ousted-from-job-in-house-vote/articleshow/104141450.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104141450.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;众议院议长凯文·麦卡锡(Kevin McCarthy)被极右翼保守派以史无前例的方式投票罢免，导致共和党领导层内部混乱。麦卡锡的竞争对手众议员马特·盖茨带头罢免他，赢得了保守派共和党人和民主党人的支持，他们认为麦卡锡不适合担任领导职务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 21:49:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/mccarthy-becomes-first-speaker-ever-to-be-ousted-from-job-in-house-vote/articleshow/104141450.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿拉斯加军用运输车相撞 造成2名士兵死亡、12人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/2-army-soldiers-killed-12-injured-as-military-transport-vehicle-crashes-in-alaska/articleshow/104141420.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104141420.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿拉斯加发生一起单车事故，造成两名美军士兵死亡、十二人受伤。士兵们乘坐军用运输车在土路上行驶时，司机失去控制，导致车辆侧翻。急救人员提供了现场治疗，受伤士兵被送往医院。陆军将调查事故原因。这是今年涉及阿拉斯加士兵的第二起致命事件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 21:40:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/2-army-soldiers-killed-12-injured-as-military-transport-vehicle-crashes-in-alaska/articleshow/104141420.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国参议员审查 TikTok 聘用字节跳动高管的事宜</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-senators-examine-tiktok-hiring-of-bytedance-executives/articleshow/104139398.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104139398.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;参议员理查德·布卢门撒尔 (Richard Blumenthal) 和玛莎·布莱克本 (Marsha Blackburn) 正在调查 TikTok 从其中国母公司聘请高级管理人员的决定。他们对 TikTok 运营的独立性及其美国用户信息的安全表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 17:05:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-senators-examine-tiktok-hiring-of-bytedance-executives/articleshow/104139398.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴西政府开始从两个亚马逊原住民领土驱逐数千人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/brazils-government-starts-expelling-thousands-of-people-from-two-amazon-indigenous-territories/articleshow/104138997.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104138997.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴西政府已开始将人们从亚马逊雨林的两个原住民领地迁移出去。目标是将土地归还给原住民。这些领土位于帕拉州，估计有超过 10,000 名非原住民非法居住在那里，从事养牛和金矿开采等活动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 16:37:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/brazils-government-starts-expelling-thousands-of-people-from-two-amazon-indigenous-territories/articleshow/104138997.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普在拒绝参加未来的共和党辩论后希望取消这些辩论</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-wants-future-republican-debates-to-be-cancelled-after-refusing-to-participate-in-them/articleshow/104138572.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104138572.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普的竞选团队敦促共和党全国委员会（RNC）取消所有剩余的初选辩论，并集中精力在明年的选举中击败乔·拜登。竞选团队还重复了毫无根据的选举舞弊指控。特朗普此前曾声称2020年大选被窃取，尽管没有证据支持这一点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 16:04:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-wants-future-republican-debates-to-be-cancelled-after-refusing-to-participate-in-them/articleshow/104138572.cms</guid></item><item><title>津巴布韦反对派抵制总统自有争议的选举以来的第一次国情咨文演讲</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/zimbabwes-opposition-boycotts-presidents-1st-state-of-the-nation-speech-since-disputed-election/articleshow/104137970.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104137970.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;津巴布韦主要反对党抵制总统埃默森·姆南加古瓦的国情咨文演讲，理由是他因被指控在八月选举中存在舞弊行为而非法。赢得第二个任期的姆南加古瓦被指控对政府批评者使用暴力和恐吓，包括逮捕一些民选反对派官员。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 15:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/zimbabwes-opposition-boycotts-presidents-1st-state-of-the-nation-speech-since-disputed-election/articleshow/104137970.cms</guid></item><item><title>突尼斯拒绝欧洲基金，称其未能达成移民协议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/tunisia-rejects-european-funds-and-says-they-fall-short-of-a-deal-for-migration-and-financial-aid/articleshow/104137655.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104137655.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;突尼斯宣布拒绝欧洲提供的资金，该资金旨在帮助该国在地中海巡逻并解决日益增加的移民船只过境问题。总统凯斯·赛义德指责欧盟没有履行之前支持突尼斯边境管制和打击走私的协议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 14:51:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/tunisia-rejects-european-funds-and-says-they-fall-short-of-a-deal-for-migration-and-financial-aid/articleshow/104137655.cms</guid></item><item><title>工会暂停罢工后，尼日利亚避免了政府关门</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/a-government-shutdown-in-nigeria-has-been-averted-after-unions-suspended-a-labour-strike/articleshow/104137485.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104137485.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尼日利亚政府工作人员在与当局进行最后一刻谈判后避免了全国范围内的罢工。原定于周二开始的罢工已暂停 30 天，但谈判仍在继续。谈判内容包括提高工人工资、向弱势家庭提供财政援助以及为公共交通燃气巴士提供资金。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 14:36:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/a-government-shutdown-in-nigeria-has-been-averted-after-unions-suspended-a-labour-strike/articleshow/104137485.cms</guid></item><item><title>斯里兰卡总统拒绝对复活节爆炸事件进行国际调查，抨击西方的双重标准</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sri-lankan-president-rejects-international-probe-into-easter-bombings-slams-west-for-its-double-standards/articleshow/104137173.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104137173.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;斯里兰卡总统拉尼尔·维克勒马辛哈拒绝对当地伊斯兰极端组织 2019 年复活节爆炸事件进行国际调查的想法。他批评西方媒体采取双重标准，并质疑为何斯里兰卡和亚洲国家受到区别对待。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 14:17:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sri-lankan-president-rejects-international-probe-into-easter-bombings-slams-west-for-its-double-standards/articleshow/104137173.cms</guid></item><item><title>亚美尼亚接受国际法院的职权范围，令莫斯科烦恼</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/armenia-to-accept-international-courts-remit-vexing-moscow/articleshow/104136878.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104136878.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;亚美尼亚议会批准了国际刑事法院（ICC）的成立章程，接受该法院的管辖。此举激怒了俄罗斯，因为国际刑事法院想要逮捕俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京。俄罗斯称这一决定“不正确”，并对亚美尼亚现任领导层表示失望。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 13:59:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/armenia-to-accept-international-courts-remit-vexing-moscow/articleshow/104136878.cms</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫表示俄罗斯尚未放弃暂停核试验</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/kremlin-says-russia-has-not-abandoned-moratorium-on-nuclear-testing/articleshow/104136247.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104136247.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;克里姆林宫表示，俄罗斯并未放弃暂停核试验，并驳回了一家国家电视台编辑提出的俄罗斯应在西伯利亚引爆核弹以警告西方的建议。俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京警告说，对俄罗斯的任何攻击都可能引发核反应。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 13:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/kremlin-says-russia-has-not-abandoned-moratorium-on-nuclear-testing/articleshow/104136247.cms</guid></item><item><title>随着动荡的投票临近，“选举恐惧”笼罩阿根廷市场</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/election-fear-stalks-argentinas-markets-as-volatile-vote-nears/articleshow/104135457.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104135457.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿根廷即将举行的总统选举给市场带来了不确定性，导致债券下跌和比索暴跌。投资者不确定如何应对激进自由主义候选人哈维尔·米雷(Javier Milei)可能当选，他提出了有利于市场的计划，但也希望关闭央行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 12:52:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/election-fear-stalks-argentinas-markets-as-volatile-vote-nears/articleshow/104135457.cms</guid></item><item><title>西班牙国王提名佩德罗·桑切斯竞选首相</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spanish-king-nominates-pedro-sanchez-for-premiership-bid/articleshow/104135115.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104135115.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;下议院议长弗朗西娜·阿门戈尔告诉记者，西班牙国王费利佩周二提名代理首相佩德罗·桑切斯接受议会投票，以决定新的任期，此前他的保守派竞争对手上周未能成为首相。如果 11 月 27 日之前没有候选人获得多数席位，则必须重新举行选举。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 12:35:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spanish-king-nominates-pedro-sanchez-for-premiership-bid/articleshow/104135115.cms</guid></item><item><title>“他们只是肉”：俄罗斯将军事和平民罪犯送上战场</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/theyre-just-meat-russia-deploys-punishment-battalions-in-echo-of-stalin/articleshow/104132631.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104132631.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据多个消息来源称，被称为“Storm-Z”小队的俄罗斯刑罚部队今年已将数百名军事和民事罪犯送往乌克兰前线，其中包括醉酒的新兵和罪犯。这些隶属于正规军的惩戒小队损失惨重，被俄罗斯国防部视为消耗性步兵。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 11:19:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/theyre-just-meat-russia-deploys-punishment-battalions-in-echo-of-stalin/articleshow/104132631.cms</guid></item><item><title>14岁少年在曼谷商场开枪 造成1死6伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/4-killed-as-14-year-old-opens-fire-at-mall-in-thailands-bangkok/articleshow/104132315.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104132315.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周二，一名14岁的枪手嫌疑人在泰国首都曼谷的一家豪华购物中心开枪，造成1人死亡、6人受伤。泰国警方已将这名青少年枪手嫌疑人拘留。此前有报道称，枪击事件已造成4人死亡。然而，收费后来被下调。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 11:12:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/4-killed-as-14-year-old-opens-fire-at-mall-in-thailands-bangkok/articleshow/104132315.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼日尔军政府称袭击加剧，圣战分子杀死 29 名士兵</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigers-junta-says-jihadis-kill-29-soldiers-as-attacks-ramp-up/articleshow/104131354.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104131354.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尼日尔军政府表示，在该国与马里边境附近，至少有 29 名尼日尔士兵被圣战分子杀害，他们正在努力结束一系列袭击。尼日尔国防部长萨利福·莫迪中将在周一晚间的一份声明中表示，100多名极端分子使用自制炸药袭击了部署在边境地区执行清理行动的西非国家安全部队。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 10:44:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigers-junta-says-jihadis-kill-29-soldiers-as-attacks-ramp-up/articleshow/104131354.cms</guid></item><item><title>土耳其在自杀式炸弹袭击后拘留近千人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-detains-nearly-1000-including-alleged-kurdish-militants-following-suicide-bomb-attack/articleshow/104130697.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104130697.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;土耳其首都发生自杀式炸弹袭击几天后，警方周二在土耳其各地的突袭中拘留了近千人，其中包括数十名据称与库尔德武装分子有联系的人。周二，警方在土耳其各地逮捕了至少 67 人，目标是涉嫌与库尔德武装分子有联系的人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 10:31:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-detains-nearly-1000-including-alleged-kurdish-militants-following-suicide-bomb-attack/articleshow/104130697.cms</guid></item><item><title>罗马尼亚决定在学校教授犹太历史和大屠杀</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/romania-marks-decision-to-teach-jewish-history-holocaust-in-schools/articleshow/104130508.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104130508.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;罗马尼亚决定将大屠杀和犹太历史纳入其学校课程。课程改革于 2021 年获得批准，被视为对第二次世界大战期间数十万罗马尼亚和乌克兰犹太人和罗姆人被杀负责的第一步。发起课程改革的立法者西尔维乌·韦克斯勒(Silviu Vexler)表示，该课程是“对所发生的事情完全承担责任的第一个真正的举措”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 10:24:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/romania-marks-decision-to-teach-jewish-history-holocaust-in-schools/articleshow/104130508.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普民事欺诈审判进入第二天，商业帝国岌岌可危</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-civil-fraud-trial-enters-second-day-as-business-empire-hangs-in-balance/articleshow/104130112.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104130112.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普在曼哈顿的民事审判仍在继续，指控他夸大资产价值以获得更优惠的贷款和保险条款。纽约州总检察长利蒂西亚·詹姆斯 (Letitia James) 正在寻求至少 2.5 亿美元的罚款，并永久禁止特朗普及其儿子在纽约经营企业。特朗普否认有不当行为，他的律师表示将上诉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 10:13:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-civil-fraud-trial-enters-second-day-as-business-empire-hangs-in-balance/articleshow/104130112.cms</guid></item><item><title>波兰和捷克共和国启动斯洛伐克边境检查以遏制移民</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/poland-czech-republic-start-slovak-border-checks-to-curb-migration/articleshow/104129028.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104129028.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波兰和捷克共和国周二表示，他们将在与斯洛伐克的边境进行检查，以遏制日益增长的非法移民。德国上周表示，将加强与波兰和捷克共和国边境的治安，以控制不断上升的非法移民数量。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 09:36:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/poland-czech-republic-start-slovak-border-checks-to-curb-migration/articleshow/104129028.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>